title: Emily Ratajkowski's hottest moments
text: Blogs Emily Ratajkowski: A look back on her hottest moments From her steamy debut in the 'Blurred Lines' music video to her role in 'Gone Girl,' blossoming supermodel Emily Ratajkowski never fails to heat things up! In honor of her 24th Birthday on June 7, take a look back at her hottest moments ... Photo: Emily Ratajkowski via Instagram./ Published: 10/9/2015 12:53:02 Emily Ratajkowski There's only one Emily Ratajkowski, but the "Blurred Lines" model clearly thinks one isn't enough as she shared two cleavage-baring mirror selfies side-by-side donning the exact same outfit, on Instagram. "Double selfie," Emily captioned the snap on Oct. 9, 2015. 1 of 42
